This is how to smallest_change of arr:
   Remember that changes is 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Remember that half is quotient of arr's length and 2

   Do this half times:
      Remember that j is diff of (diff of arr's length and 1) and i
      When item i in arr is not item j in arr, then:
         Increase changes
      End when
      Increase i
   End do

   The answer is changes
